## Minimal memory footprint for pgrx

## 1 normal scheduler, 2 dirty CPU, 1 dirty IO
+S 1:1
+SDcpu 2:2
+SDio 1

## Disable busy-wait (saves CPU + reduces allocator pressure)
+sbwt none
+sbwtdcpu none
+sbwtdio none
+swt very_low

## Memory allocator tuning
+MBas aobf
+MHas aobf

## Kernel poll
+K true
